OL,3,CFears that Ofsted's proposed grading
OL,4,Cscale is 'rehash of dangerous system'
OL,6,FThe sister of headteacher Ruth Perry
OL,7,Fhas said she is worried that new
OL,8,FOfsted proposals for inspecting
OL,9,Fschools are a "rehash" of the
OL,10,F"dangerous" system they are supposed
OL,11,Fto replace.
OL,13,FSchools in England could be graded
OL,14,Facross a variety of different areas `
OL,15,Fincluding attendance and inclusion `
OL,16,Fusing a colour-coded five-point scale.
