OL,6,FSchools would receive ratings ` from
OL,7,Fthe red coloured "causing concern" to
OL,8,Forange coloured "attention needed",
OL,9,Fthrough the green shades of "secure",
OL,10,F"strong" and "exemplary" ` for each
