OL,6,FPreviously, Ofsted awarded one of four
OL,7,Fsingle-phrase inspection judgments:
OL,8,Foutstanding, good, requires
OL,9,Fimprovement and inadequate.
OL,11,FThe reforms follow criticism of the
OL,12,Finspection system following the death
OL,13,Fof headteacher Mrs Perry who took her
OL,14,Fown life after an Ofsted report
OL,15,Fdowngraded her Caversham Primary
OL,16,FSchool in Reading from the highest to
OL,17,Fthe lowest overall effectiveness
OL,18,Frating over safeguarding concerns.
