OL,3,CFears that Ofsted's proposed grading
OL,4,Cscale is 'rehash of dangerous system'
OL,6,FHer sister Professor Julia Waters said
OL,7,Fthat while the new model has some
OL,8,Fimprovements, it "retains many of the
OL,9,Fdangerous features of the previous
OL,10,Fsystem, while introducing a series of
OL,11,Fchanges with potential new risks to
OL,12,Fthe wellbeing of teachers and
OL,13,Fheadteachers".
OL,15,FProf Waters said: "My sister Ruth
OL,16,FPerry died as the result of a rude and
OL,17,Fintimidating Ofsted inspection, and
OL,18,Fits disproportionate consequences on
OL,19,Fher and her school.
