OL,6,FProf Waters said the proposal appears
OL,7,Fto have fed the single-word judgments
OL,8,F"through an online thesaurus", adding
OL,9,Fthat "other elements of the report
OL,10,Fcard design are ill-thought-through
OL,11,Fand potentially dangerous".
OL,13,FUnder the proposals from the
OL,14,Finspectorate, at least eight areas of
OL,15,Fa school's provision could be
OL,16,Fevaluated and graded ` accompanied by
OL,17,Fshort summaries of inspectors'
OL,18,Ffindings ` in a report card for
OL,19,Fparents.
