OL,6,FThe proposed evaluation areas would be
OL,7,Fleadership and governance, curriculum,
OL,8,Fdeveloping teaching, achievement,
OL,9,Fbehaviour and attitudes, attendance,
OL,10,Fpersonal development and wellbeing,
OL,11,Fand inclusion.
OL,13,FSchools which have early years
OL,14,Fprovision or a sixth form would also
OL,15,Fbe graded separately on these areas.
OL,17,FSafeguarding would not be graded with
OL,18,Fthe five-point scale and instead it
OL,19,Fwould be assessed as either met or not
OL,20,Fmet under the plans.
