OL,6,FThe proposals have been criticised by
OL,7,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,8,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, who said
OL,9,Fthey "suggest an inspectorate
OL,10,Fdetermined to hold on to a model of
OL,11,Finspection that is long past its sell-
OL,12,Fby date".
OL,14,FAnd Pepe Di'Iasio, general secretary
OL,15,Fof the Association of School and
OL,16,FCollege Leaders (ASCL), said the
OL,17,Fproposed school report cards "appear
OL,18,Fto be even worse than the single-word
OL,19,Fjudgments they replace".
