OL,6,FFrom November, it is proposed that
OL,7,FOfsted will no longer carry out
OL,8,Fungraded inspections of state schools
OL,9,Fwhich means every school will know
OL,10,Fthat its next routine Ofsted
OL,11,Finspection will be a full, graded one.
OL,13,FUnder the proposals, the watchdog will
OL,14,Falso include more contextual data in
OL,15,Finspections and reports ` such as
OL,16,Flearner characteristics, absence and
OL,17,Fattendance figures, and local area
OL,18,Fdemographics.
